THIRD-PARTY SOFTWARE
------------------------------------------------------------------------------

Goel° bundles the following third-party components inside the application. Each
is redistributed under its own license; the full texts are in
THIRD-PARTY-NOTICES.md, which ships with the app and must accompany any
redistribution.

  Component                     Purpose                         License
  ---------------------------   -----------------------------   ---------------
  libtorrent-rasterbar 2.0.x    BitTorrent engine               BSD-3-Clause
  Boost 1.9x                    (used by libtorrent)            BSL-1.0
  OpenSSL 3.x (libssl/crypto)   TLS + crypto for torrent/SFTP   Apache-2.0
  libssh2 1.11.x                SFTP engine + browser           BSD-3-Clause
  GRDB.swift 6.x                SQLite persistence              MIT
  Sparkle 2.x                   Auto-update framework           MIT
  yt-dlp                        Optional video-site resolver    The Unlicense

The system libraries Goel° links from macOS (libcurl, libsqlite3, the Swift
runtime, and Apple frameworks) are provided by the operating system and are not
redistributed by this project.
